{
  "description": "A wide, panoramic view captures a city nestled along a coastline during a vibrant sunset. The sky is dominated by dramatic, dark clouds streaked with hues of purple, pink, and grey. Below the cloud cover, a bright orange and yellow band marks the horizon where the sun is setting over the water. The city sprawls beneath, with buildings appearing as a dense collection of lights and shapes. A dark, hilly foreground provides a sense of elevation and perspective. The overall impression is one of expansive landscape and a beautiful, but potentially stormy, atmospheric condition.",
